-----------------------------
| Core Domain Relationships |
-----------------------------

User
 ├── has many Addresses
 ├── has many Prescriptions
 ├── has many Orders
 └── has many SubstitutionConsents

Prescription
 ├── belongs to User
 ├── has many PrescriptionItems
 └── can be linked to Orders

PrescriptionItem
 ├── belongs to Prescription
 └── references Medicine (requested)

Medicine
 ├── has many ChemistPrices
 └── referenced in OrderItems

Chemist
 ├── has many ChemistPrices
 └── fulfills Orders

ChemistPrice
 ├── belongs to Chemist
 └── belongs to Medicine

Order
 ├── belongs to User
 ├── belongs to Chemist
 ├── has many OrderItems
 └── has one Delivery

OrderItem
 ├── belongs to Order
 └── belongs to Medicine

SubstitutionConsent
 ├── belongs to User
 └── optionally linked to PrescriptionItem

Delivery
 └── belongs to Order
